{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-2", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "不過別離", "storyInfo": "城中飢荒爆發，對維多利亞人的仇恨也被刻意煽動起來。庫林試圖分發存糧以維持秩序，而涅梅絲接過庫林尋找提奧的託付，在四處尋找無果後碰到了拉芙希妮。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g1_citystreets_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1695_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1696_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "step", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……嗯？", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好多人……", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉！呃……借過一下——", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——啊！", "name": "提奧"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——米林頓街我也去過了，早就什麼也沒有了！雖然店門都開著，但貨架全是空的，連個袋子都沒有！", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "克拉馬那傢伙說這邊有庫存，我才跑了五條街過來——結果還是連根羽獸毛都看不見！", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還不如回去拿弩，翻出去崗哨，到黑林裡打點獵，或許還能在餓死之前吃點真正的葷腥……", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……什麼？", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看你是餓瘋了，去黑林才是真的去送死！", "name": "憤怒的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒發瘋？！說得像你就知道什麼了一樣！", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼不知道？拉格蘭街的糧店，艾瑪開的，你知道吧？", "name": "憤怒的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那家我還沒去呢，怎麼了？", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我先去的那裡。雖然也沒糧食，但聽艾瑪的說法，這件事和*維多利亞粗口*的維多利亞人脫不了關係！", "name": "憤怒的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的混蛋封鎖我們，這又不是第一天了，他們當然該負責。這有什麼稀奇的？", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞的間諜已經滲透進納斯爾紗了！", "name": "憤怒的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你再說一遍？！", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾瑪去農業地塊的時候親眼看見了被火燒過的痕跡，深池還在調查呢！", "name": "憤怒的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*維多利亞粗口*！塔拉獨立之後我們就該馬上打回去！", "name": "急切的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1687_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過有句話你說對了，你確實該回去拿你的弩，但不是為了打獵，而是為了找出那些幫維多利亞人辦事的叛徒！", "name": "憤怒的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果讓我抓到他，肯定不是用弩箭穿心這麼簡單就結束了。", "name": "憤怒的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1689_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）好像是這些店裡的糧食供應斷了……", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）雖然我幫庫林先生囤積了一些馬鈴薯，但可能還是不夠……", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）這裡人太多了，還是走另一條路吧。", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）還有好多人都拿著武器……", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）他們是想圍剿維多利亞間諜嗎？城裡沒有糧食……跟維多利亞人也有關係嗎？", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）但我……", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）我……", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒關係的。我是庫林先生的學徒。大家都知道這件事。", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別害怕，提奧。大家不會拿你怎麼樣的。", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提奧努力矮下身子，從人群中擠出去，來到街道的轉角處。他靈活地從一條狹窄暗道裡穿過，來到石磚牆體的另一面。"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘈雜的人聲逐漸從他的耳邊退去。"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g1_citystreets_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "style": "slider", "inverse": "true", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你看，提奧，沒人找你的麻煩。", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林先生肯定還在忙紅龍雕像的事，等他反應過來，其他店裡肯定也什麼都不剩了。", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我得幫忙。", "name": "提奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "step1", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "step1", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們先把這些東西拿去吃，分給周圍的鄰居，讓他們不要急。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你自己怎麼辦？還有涅梅絲，她會不會沒得吃？", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比起把糧食都給我們，你不如跟那些人一起去抓維多利亞間諜。否則無法從根本上解決問題，不是嗎？", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "庫林", "content": " ……我會去的，也麻煩你這樣告訴其他人。"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "庫林", "content": "這些東西你們也先拿著。"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲在領袖的身邊，為你們吃些苦也是應該的。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我……那我就不跟你客氣了！", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……庫林，你肯定還有別的存糧，對不對？", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，你怎麼知道糧食供應會中斷？是不是涅梅絲提前跟你說了什麼——", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅里，你在說什麼啊！", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不要就算了。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有誰能證明你或者涅梅絲不是間諜？你們合夥養大了一個維多利亞人的孩子！", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……滾。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我憑什麼滾？你心虛什麼？你——", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林，我聽說你在發糧，真是太及時了！你發的東西都在哪裡呢？", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下的都在這裡了。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別打斷我。庫林，你還沒回答我的問題。", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能說的我都已經說了。你要是覺得這點馬鈴薯弄髒你的手，就把袋子給別人。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你？！", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅里，你到底要不要？不要就給我，想要的人多的是，別不識好歹。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "給我——", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憑什麼？", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是不要嗎，給我！", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想得美——", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovementsp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.7, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.52", "scale": 1.1, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_exsheath"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knife", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.4, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃——啊！", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_orangefall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "袋子裡的馬鈴薯都很小，沒有一個長成正常的橢圓形。"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的手臂？！", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天啊，流血了！羅里，你怎麼能對同胞下手？！", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我、我——", "name": "陰沉的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_axeimp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "把刀放下。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別逼我用這把錘子對付你。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1686_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_bellfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不、不愧是你啊，庫林。", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅里的狀態不太對，我跟上去看看……自從他收藏的那些古董在戰爭中被一把火燒了之後，他就一直瘋瘋癲癲的。", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "至於他的刀——他的刀你就收起來吧，庫林，別再還給他了。", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_footstep_stonestep", "volume": 0.6, "channel": "wstep", "loop": "false"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "wstep", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林，我……唉……", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傷口不深，過來，我先幫你止血。糧食的事，等涅梅絲回來，我請她想想辦法。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道……嘶……我知道，你是真的把自己有的都拿出來了。", "name": "焦急的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1752_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "焦急的居民", "content": "你也就是看起來兇巴巴的——"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 60.0, "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "焦急的居民", "content": "嘶！"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "少說話，節省力氣。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "家裡可能還剩一點玉米粉，我去找找。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你拿著，然後我送你回去。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g10_indoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "庫林，你和提奧還好——", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……地上怎麼有血？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅里失控砍傷了人。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提奧呢？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提奧一早就出去了——", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#9$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……糟了！", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#5$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "涅梅絲", "content": "你——"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "涅梅絲", "content": "唉，算了，沒有人想得到事情會突然變成這樣。"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城裡現在怎麼樣了？", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#11$1"}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到處都在傳是維多利亞人破壞了農業地塊，納斯爾紗已經快失控了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，你之前幫提奧出了一次頭後就沒人敢欺負他，你才放心讓他到處跑。但這次……不一樣。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我現在就去找他——", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你的雕像還來得及嗎？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "庫林", "content": "雕像得在夏末節前完工，只剩下一點時間了……"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "庫林", "content": "該死，該死！"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提奧的事我會去處理，你就專心做好手中的事吧。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#2$1"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "庫林"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1697_1#10$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g1_citystreets_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看見提奧了嗎？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "提奧？那個孩子又跑去哪裡偷懶了？庫林太寵他了，你真的應該唸一下他……", "name": "友善的居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1688_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g3_dragonsquare_d", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 310, "prop